ving the woman to face her survival with a new admirer while pining for her lost love.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":0.4572,"vote_count":158,"poster_path":"/9gJXoE2kkyFUflet4VzjQbMMwV8.jpg","release_date":"1938-12-17","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/216KAu0V0FSZAOMzJXJx4fwv5AG.jpg","original_title":"Hôtel du Nord","original_language":"fr"},{"id":48385,"adult":false,"title":"Indestructible Man","video":false,"overview":"A scientific experiment involving subjecting a corpse to an extreme charge of electricity accidentally revives an executed criminal and makes him impervious to harm, allowing him to seek revenge on his former partners, and deal similarly with anyone else who gets in his way.","genre_ids":[80,27,878],"popularity":0.4374,"vote_count":54,"poster_path":"/kcD0kG86GK2mUHjNf6QoDfwtnxd.jpg","release_date":"1956-03-24","vote_average":4.25,"backdrop_path":"/3bAoBfuCIVbIRLOBL8Nqerdycuz.jpg","original_title":"Indestructible Man","original_language":"en"},{"id":705399,"adult":false,"title":"Voices","video":false,"overview":"A troubled young man deals with the competing voices in his head.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1854,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/yOFUDQje4LdGrYVrFwCkEnaNvPF.jpg","release_date":"2020-05-22","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/qe7OgEW3lA6a95Uh5iD49O0gT8y.jpg","original_title":"Voices","original_language":"en"},{"id":48617,"adult":false,"title":"Father and Daughter","video":false,"overview":"A father says goodbye to his young daughter. In time the daughter grows old, but within her there is always a deep longing for her father.","genre_ids":[16,18],"popularity":0.1831,"vote_count":184,"poster_path":"/dQOSA51phS7zqRqSHMXo67irfxo.jpg","release_date":"2001-04-19","vote_average":7.503,"backdrop_path":"/7LJDiAeEK5FFHR7kOIYmFPgNKNf.jpg","original_title":"Father and Daughter","original_language":"xx"},{"id":513409,"adult":false,"title":"Earthquake Bird","video":false,"overview":"Tokyo, Japan, 1989. Lucy Fly, a foreigner who works as a t