hing for that something missing in her life, finds it in El Salvador, hooking up with three nuns and a heartful of ache, love, and horror in the midst of a civil war. This is a true story of the four American churchwomen murdered in the Central American countryside, and the indifference of the American government to their sad and desperate story.","genre_ids":[10770,18],"popularity":0.2968,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1983-12-05","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Choices of the Heart","original_language":"en"},{"id":48481,"adult":false,"title":"Five","video":false,"overview":"The film's storyline involves five survivors, one woman and four men, of an atomic bomb disaster. The five come together at a remote, isolated hillside house, where they try to figure out how to survive.","genre_ids":[878,18],"popularity":0.2914,"vote_count":38,"poster_path":"/awMJBJpywUl7u75rLGohrRZ41wl.jpg","release_date":"1951-04-25","vote_average":6.592,"backdrop_path":"/5eLRW1lwivUdoflnb3wt0PcqAQc.jpg","original_title":"Five","original_language":"en"},{"id":513692,"adult":false,"title":"Raging Fire","video":false,"overview":"Cheung Sung-bong is a highly respected cop with a long history of success in dangerous cases. However, his past soon comes back to haunt him when a former protégé resurfaces, seeking revenge.","genre_ids":[28,80,53,12,9648],"popularity":2.6559,"vote_count":284,"poster_path":"/flFQEHlW4omcU47jwgNKPw7SpF3.jpg","release_date":"2021-07-28","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/qLtREPyJgxewgK3l68epEQeHTVR.jpg","original_title":"怒火","original_language":"cn"},{"id":48773,"adult":false,"title":"Game of Death II","video":false,"overview":"In this dark tale of revenge, Bruce Lee \"returns\" as Billy Lo, whose best friend Chin Ku dies of a sudden illness. But suspicion of foul play arises when a gang tries to steal Ku's coffin at the funeral using a helicopter. When Lo's younger brother Lo hears about the incident, he leaves his Buddhist 