9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Léon: The Professional | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Léon, the top hit man in New York, has earned a rep as an effective \"cleaner\". But when his next-door neighbors are wiped out by a loose-cannon DEA agent, he becomes the unwilling custodian of 12-year-old Mathilda. Before long, Mathilda's thoughts turn to revenge, and she considers following in Léon's footsteps."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148155/l-on-the-professional"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Léon: The Professional"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Léon, the top hit man in New York, has earned a rep as an effective \"cleaner\". But when his next-door neighbors are wiped out by a loose-cannon DEA agent, he becomes the unwilling custodian of 12-year-old Mathilda. Before long, Mathilda's thoughts turn to revenge, and she considers following in Léon's footsteps."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148155/l-on-the-professional"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bxB2q91nKYp8JNzqE7t7TWBVupB.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Léon: The Professional"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Léon, the top hit man in New York, has earned a rep as an effective \"cleaner\". But when his next-door neighbors are wiped out by a loose-cannon DEA agent, he becomes the unwilling custodian of 12-year-old Mathilda. Before long, Mathilda's thoughts turn to revenge, and she considers foll